.head 3 +  ! Function: GetItemNumber
.head 4 -  Description: This takes the passed item Type, Variety and Cultivar and returns the stock item number
.head 4 +  Returns 
.head 5 -  Boolean: 
.head 4 +  Parameters 
.head 5 -  String: sVarietyType
.head 5 -  String: sVariety
